                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Ascending Diluc gains increased CRIT Rate, synergizing with this weapon's sub-stats and decreasing the CRIT sub-stat demand of artifacts. Additionally, Diluc can reliably trigger this weapon's special effect against groups of enemies while set as the main DPS. This weapon is a decent choice among 4-star weapons.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 41,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Xinyan_icon.png",
                      "name": "Xinyan",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Once Xinyan unlocks C2, a portion of Physical DMG from Elemental Bursts is guaranteed to CRIT. With Xinyan as a secondary main DPS, she can focus on stacking ATK and CRIT DMG, which makes this weapon an ideal choice by synergizing the CRIT DMG boost from its sub-stats.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
